name: Yet to be Determined
description:
Submission for My First Game Jam Winter 2022. 

Game is currently still in development. Current state of the game is not meant to be representative of the finished product, it is essentially a beta demo. The demo might be prone to errors or crashes. Whatever.

There is not much to it except for walking atm, but hopefully you enjoy the ambiance.  The rain is all randomly generated. I'm proud of that.

Use arrow keys to move.

More to be posted soon.

Credits to https://shiptoaster.itch.io/ and my awesome girlfriend for the amazing art. Couldn't have done it without you guys.
